          <formatted-text>
            <run>This is our quantity sold by day throughout the fiscal year 2017 with a forecast going through January 2021. Due to the trend in the data for 2017 being relatively minor, the forecast for January 2018 has a high margin for error. More data or a more definitive relationship in our data would provide for a better forecast</run>
